+reagent-name-caramel = caramel
+reagent-desc-caramel = A sweet, smooth mixture created from heated sugar.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-caramel = caramel ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-caramel = Sweet, salty, and creamy!
+
+reagent-name-chopped-nuts = chopped nuts
+reagent-desc-chopped-nuts = Delicious nuts packed with protien. Much more mixable.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-apple-caramel = apple caramel ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-apple-caramel = Nothing goes together like caramel, apples, and ice cream.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-caramel-fudge = caramel fudge ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-caramel-fudge = A deep, rich flavor with caramel to lighten it up!
+
+reagent-name-icecream-cherry = cherry ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-cherry = Just as sweet as strawberry!
+
+reagent-name-icecream-chocolate = chocolate ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-chocolate = A classic staple only few can enjoy.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-cobbler = berry cobbler ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-cobbler = It's a cobbler that got crammed into ice cream which is crammed into a glass.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-coffee = coffee ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-coffee = A cold pick-me-up.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-cookiedough = cookie dough ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-cookiedough = A chunky ice cream covered in edible cookie dough!
+
+reagent-name-icecream-greentea = green tea ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-greentea = A refreshing and soothing dessert.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-mint = mint ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-mint = Based on the classic mint ice cream with faux chocolate.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-neapolitan = neapolitan Ice Cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-neapolitan = An ice cream so simple no one knows its true origins.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-pistachio = pistachio ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-pistachio = For the real ice cream nuts.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-rockyroad = rocky road ice cream
+eagent-desc-icecream-rockyroad = It's an ice cream with a rough texture and rich flavor.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-tower = tower of ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-tower = Babel has met its match.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-vegan = vegan ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-vegan = A soy-based ice cream with no animal products.
+
+reagent-name-icecream-watermelon = watermelon ice cream
+reagent-desc-icecream-watermelon = The taste of a refreshing Summer in one glass.
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-rainbow = rainbow sherbet
+reagent-desc-sherbet-rainbow = The titan of sherbets.
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-lemon = lemon sherbet
+reagent-desc-sherbet-lemon = The classic sweet, tart, and sour fruit now really cold.
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-lime = lime sherbet
+reagent-desc-sherbet-lime = Lemon sherbert's little brother.
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-orange = orange sherbet
+reagent-desc-sherbet-orange = Orange you glad its sherbet?
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-pineapple = pineapple sherbet
+reagent-desc-sherbet-pineapple = Not only does it look like a vaction, it taste like it too.
+
+reagent-name-sherbet-raspberry = raspberry sherbert
+reagent-desc-sherbet-raspberry = Give them the old razzle dazzle!
+
+reagent-name-slush-blue-raspberry = blue raspberry slush
+reagent-desc-slush-blue-raspberry = You can feel your teeth chattering.
+
+reagent-name-slush-cherry = cherry slush
+reagent-desc-slush-cherry = While it's rumored to be red, it's typically white.
+
+reagent-name-slush-cola = cola slush
+reagent-desc-slush-cola = Space cola in the form of a brain freeze.
+
+reagent-name-tropical-sunday = tropical sunday
+reagent-desc-tropical-sunday = Kick back and relax.
